        "content": "<p>While reviewing the DRM abstractions, I noticed a pattern:</p>\n<div class=\"codehilite\" data-code-language=\"Rust\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"k\">match</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">x</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">{</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"nb\">Err</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"n\">e</span><span class=\"p\">)</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">=&gt;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">e</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"n\">to_errno</span><span class=\"p\">(),</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"nb\">Ok</span><span class=\"p\">(())</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">=&gt;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"mi\">0</span>\n<span class=\"p\">}</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<p>This seems to come up in other abstractions too. Time for a helper for this..?</p>",
        "id": 512175578,
        "sender_full_name": "Alyssa Rosenzweig",
